    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT382-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">paruvavaraviṉkaṇ vēṟupaṭṭa talaimakaḷait tōḻi “paruvam aṉṟu vampu”
                    eṉṟu vaṟpuṟīiyatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante, saying “it is not the season,
                    [it is] out of time”, encouraging HER, who had changed at the coming of the
                    season. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT382">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> taṇṭuḷik kēṟṟa paiṅkoṭi mullai</l>
                    <l> mukaitalai tiṟanta nāṟṟam putaṉmicaip</l>
                    <l> pūmali taḷavamoṭu tēṅkamaḻpu kañala</l>
                    <l> vampum peyyumār maḻaiyē vampaṉṟu</l>
                    <l> kāritu paruva māyiṉ</l>
                    <l> vārā rōnaṅ kāta lōrē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l> Out of time too indeed rains the rain,</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> so that the jasmine in fresh creepers, exposed to the cool drops,</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> is dense, smelling of honey, together with the red jasmine</l>
                    <l rend="indent8"> full of flowers,</l>
                    <l rend="indent2"> on the fragrant shrubs, where the bud heads have opened.</l>
                    <l> If it is not out of time [and] this [is] the rainy season</l>
                    <l> won't he come, our lover?</l>


                </lg>
            </div>
